{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231030/extras/header_gameplay.png?t=1729617160\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Mountain Hook is a simple, zen-like time-waster about scaling giant stone towers. It's best enjoyed with a podcast and your favorite snack as you ascend into the skies - flirt with gravity and let the real world pass by on the wind</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231030/extras/mountain_hook_example.gif?t=1729617160\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Pick your route up each new mountain and take as many risks as you think necessary to reach the summit. Toss a few of your sticky explosives if you need to create some space and throw in the occasional back-flip simply because you can.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Note: </strong>Mountain Hook supports mouse and keyboard but was designed to be played with a pad for the most satisfying swing</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231030/extras/header_features.png?t=1729617160\" /></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A grappling hook with playfully satisfying swinging physics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Some explosives, in case you need to get creative</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A genuinely pointless and risky back-flip ability</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Predefined challenge mountains to get you accustomed</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unlock-able character customization options</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Gamepad support with configurable buttons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Endless, procedurally generated monoliths, begging to be tamed</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Mountain Hook is the work of a solo developer. If you experience any issues, get in touch and I'll address them as soon as possible.</i></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231030/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1729617160","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231030/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1729617160","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231030/16fe78a1f26ff33ec75103b3a9c0f7c603722a50/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1729617160","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231030/16fe78a1f26ff33ec75103b3a9c0f7c603722a50/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1729617160","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231030/extras/header_gameplay.png?t=1729617160\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Mountain Hook is a simple, zen-like time-waster about scaling giant stone towers. It's best enjoyed with a podcast and your favorite snack as you ascend into the skies - flirt with gravity and let the real world pass by on the wind</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231030/extras/mountain_hook_example.gif?t=1729617160\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Pick your route up each new mountain and take as many risks as you think necessary to reach the summit. Toss a few of your sticky explosives if you need to create some space and throw in the occasional back-flip simply because you can.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Note: </strong>Mountain Hook supports mouse and keyboard but was designed to be played with a pad for the most satisfying swing</p><h2 class=\"bb_ta